7module serial_adder #(WIDTH=32) (
8        input  [WIDTH-1:0] a,
9        input  [WIDTH-1:0] b,
10        input  cin,
11        output [WIDTH-1:0] s,
12        output cout);
13
14    wire [WIDTH:0] c;
15

17        full_adder fa(a[i], b[i], c[i], s[i], c[i+1]);
18    endgenerate

1module full_adder (
2        input a,
3        input b,
4        input cin,
5        output s,
6        output cout);
7    assign s = a^b^cin;
8    assign cout = (a&b) | (b&cin) | (a&cin);
9endmodule;
